OL,3,CSark Seigneur 'perplexed' after
OL,4,Celectricity boss threatens to cut
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FSark's Seigneur says he is "perplexed"
OL,8,Fby a claim made by the owner of Sark
OL,9,FElectricity Limited (SEL) that he
OL,10,Fthreatened company staff after
OL,11,Fattempts were made to gain access to
OL,12,Fhis property.
OL,14,FChristopher Beaumont dismisses the
OL,15,Fallegation, which arose after SEL
OL,16,Fowner Alan Witney-Price stated that he
OL,17,Fwanted to sever the Seigneur's supply,
OL,18,Fclaiming he was denying them the
OL,19,Fopportunity to maintain the safety of
OL,20,Fthe utility company's operations.
