OL,3,CSark Seigneur 'perplexed' after
OL,4,Celectricity boss threatens to cut
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FThis follows Mr Beaumont's refusal to
OL,8,Fpay the 60p of legal levies added to
OL,9,Fevery unit of electricity in September.
OL,11,FThe Seigneur was not alone in his
OL,12,Fboycott as Sark's government, Chief
OL,13,FPleas, and a number of residents also
OL,14,Frefused to pay, with prices ballooning
OL,15,Fto #1.14 per unit.
OL,17,FAn investigation carried out by the
OL,18,Fisland's Price Control Commissioner
OL,19,Ffound that the rise was "neither fair
OL,20,Fnor reasonable" and the cost was
OL,21,Freduced to 52p per unit.
