OL,3,CSark Seigneur 'perplexed' after
OL,4,Celectricity boss threatens to cut
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FLast month, SEL asked the regulator to
OL,8,Fincrease prices back up to 92p per
OL,9,Funit.
OL,11,FMr Beaumont says that while SEL have
OL,12,Fequipment on his land, they have no
OL,13,Flegal guarantee of being able to
OL,14,Faccess his land without permission,
OL,15,Fbut that he "feels for" the staff
OL,16,Fbeing asked to try and access his
OL,17,Fproperty and others, which have also
OL,18,Fbeen threatened with disconnection for
OL,19,Fnot paying the levies in September.
