OL,3,CSark Seigneur 'perplexed' after
OL,4,Celectricity boss threatens to cut
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FThe Seigneur says that while
OL,8,Fdisconnecting homes would make Sark
OL,9,F"unliveable", he does not believe
OL,10,Fcutting off the electricity supply is
OL,11,Fa realistic prospect.
OL,13,FIn a statement last week, Chief Pleas
OL,14,Falso said that SEL had "no
OL,15,Fjustification for any disruption to
OL,16,Fsupply".
