OL,4,Celectricity boss threatens to cut
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FChief Pleas and SEL both consented to
OL,8,Fappointing Begbies Traynor as the
OL,9,Fvaluer in a move towards a compulsory
OL,10,Fpurchase.
OL,12,FThe way the company is valued will be
OL,13,Fdecided at a hearing, which is likely
OL,14,Fto be in the New Year.
